---
title: Rosemary Pork Kebabs with Chargrilled Veggies
description: These pork kebabs have a delicious East meets West fusion flavour rolled up in them, with fragrant rosemary playing off against the classic combination of honey and soy. Along with hearty chargrilled veg and some all-important condiment action in the form of aioli, we’re calling this meeting a win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b72625c30006c6a8a28a6a2-0933a538.jpg
